ambil berat terhadap saya?

504
00:33:45,560 --> 00:33:47,000
Awak sentiasa
ambil berat terhadap orang lain.

505
00:33:50,479 --> 00:33:52,920
Awak fikirkan Lei Yuzheng saja.

506
00:33:53,880 --> 00:33:54,920
Awak ini memang si jahat!

507
00:33:57,040 --> 00:33:57,800
Apa yang awak cakap?

508
00:34:15,639 --> 00:34:16,520
Fanlu.

509
00:34:18,320 --> 00:34:19,239
Fanlu!

510
00:34:20,360 --> 00:34:21,479
Awak tak apa-apa?

511
00:34:22,000 --> 00:34:22,840
Fanlu!

512
00:34:22,840 --> 00:34:24,080
Saya membawa awak ke hospital, okey?

513
00:34:25,239 --> 00:34:26,959
Mari kita pergi ke hospital!

514
00:34:27,120 --> 00:34:27,959
Fanlu!

515
00:34:41,399 --> 00:34:42,239
Fanlu.

516
00:34:43,840 --> 00:34:44,919
Saya bersalah terhadap awak.

517
00:34:45,320 --> 00:34:46,639
Bolehkah awak memaafkan saya?

518
00:35:03,399 --> 00:35:04,199
Ayah.

519
00:35:12,040 --> 00:35:15,879
Anak, kenapa menjadi begini?

520
00:35:16,399 --> 00:35:18,399
Ayah, saya sendiri...

521
00:35:20,239 --> 00:35:21,719
Saya sendiri terjatuh.

522
00:35:23,959 --> 00:35:26,919
Lin Xiangyuan, awak beritahu ayah,

523
00:35:27,639 --> 00:35:28,760
apa dah berlaku?

524
00:35:28,840 --> 00:35:30,120
Kenapa kandungannya dah gugur?

525
00:35:30,239 --> 00:35:31,040
Ayah,

526
00:35:32,320 --> 00:35:33,840
Fanlu terjatuh secara tidak sengaja.

527
00:35:34,719 --> 00:35:35,879
Dia betul-betul terjatuh?

528
00:35:36,399 --> 00:35:37,719
Ayah, benar ini.

529
00:35:38,000 --> 00:35:39,719
Saya tak berani
melayan Fanlu dengan buruk.

530
00:35:48,479 --> 00:35:50,000
Ayah beritahu awak.

531
00:35:51,280 --> 00:35:53,239
Ayah yang memupuk awak

532
00:35:53,600 --> 00:35:55,600
dan jelas apa yang awak fikirkan.

533
00:35:57,239 --> 00:35:59,959
Baik awak setia terhadap Fanlu.

534
00:36:01,320 --> 00:36:03,080
Fanlu anak perempuan kesayangan ayah.

535
00:36:03,600 --> 00:36:05,120
Jika awak melukainya,

536
00:36:06,800 --> 00:36:08,360
ayah tidak akan memaafkan awak.

537
00:36:41,821 --> 00:36:44,790
(Lei Ting)

538
00:36:50,520 --> 00:36:53,399
